            , was indicted for <rs id="t18130113-46-off258" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130113-46-off258" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130113-46-off258" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
