                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-46-off258 t18130113-46-cd259"></join>, eight trusses of hay, value 24 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130113-46-victim427" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Moodey
                  <interp inst="t18130113-46-victim427" type="surname" value="Moodey"></interp>
